Title: Series: The Life of the Virgin
Description: The Flight into Egypt, within a dense wood, the Virgin and Child on a donkey, St Joseph on foot; on the left a date palm tree and a stag, on the top right a cloud with fifteen angels Engraving
Curator's comments: After a series of 20 woodcuts on the Life of the Virgin by Albrecht Dürer. For impressions by Dürer on same subject see E.2.184; 1895,0122.654; 1895,0122.634.
